#{124}{}{Hey, don't be stupid! The Sheriff himself gave the permission to sell here, though threatened to throw out of the city, if any fuss happens because of me. Besides, the local caravan won't approve. Well, then... It's not fair! I have honestly earned my goods and dragged them here on my back. And now it turns out that because of this I17m a criminal. All because the factory does not want to recognize the most important thing - that their product is much worse than pre-war one. You just try it and will immediately feel the difference! Want some?}
{124}{}{嘿，别傻了！警长本人同意在这里出售，尽管他威胁说，如果因为我而引起任何骚动，他将被赶出这个城市。另外，当地的商队不会批准的。那么。。。这不公平！我真的挣到了我的货，把它们背在我的背上拖到这里。现在发现因为这个我是个罪犯。这一切都是因为工厂不想认识到最重要的一点――他们的产品比战前差得多。你只要尝试一下，就会立刻感受到不同！想要一些吗？}
#{125}{}{Unlike your goods, the products of the factory do not stink radiation from a mile away.}
