#{128}{}{[He starts to look tired] Maybe... But listen. In the village, where me and my son are from, is nobody left, 'cause to live there became impossible. One day I found out about an abandoned truck of Nuka-Cola. The batch in my wagon is all that was there. Honestly. I just wanted to make a quick buck and get out of town. Me and my son are left without shelter and food, we need something to buy supplements and ammunition with. In other circumstances, I wouldn't have to climb into irradiated truck. Besides, bottles not so heavily irradiated that anyone would notice.}
{128}{}{[他开始看起来很累]也许。。。但是听着。在我和我儿子的村子里，一个人也没有了，因为在那里生活是不可能的。有一天我发现一辆废弃的努卡可乐卡车。我马车里的那一批就是那里的全部。说真的？我只是想赚个快钱然后离开这个城市。我和我儿子没有住所和食物，我们需要一些东西来买补充剂和弹药。在其他情况下，我就不必爬上卡车了。此外，瓶子没有那么严重的辐射，任何人都会注意到。}
#{129}{}{Then I can buy all your cola.}
